---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout>
  <main
    class="bg-gray-50 py-24 mt-8 pb-24 transition-all duration-[360ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(0.2,0.9,0.2,1)] origin-top"
  >
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Support & Help Center
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Find answers to common questions below. If you can't find what you're
          looking for, we're here to help.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 max-w-[900px] mx-auto mb-16">
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 text-left transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-gray-300"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">
            How do I install AutoLister AI?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            AutoLister AI is a Chrome Extension. You can install it in seconds
            from the Chrome Web Store. Just click the "Get Extension" button on
            our homepage or in the navigation bar. After adding it to Chrome, we
            recommend pinning it to your toolbar for easy access!
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 text-left transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-gray-300"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">
            How do I use the extension on Vinted?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            Once installed, navigate to the listing creation page on Vinted. As
            you upload your photos, you'll see the Generate button. Click it,
            and our AI will instantly generate a compelling title and
            description for you to review and use.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 text-left transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-gray-300"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">
            The AutoLister icon isn't appearing. What should I do?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            First, try refreshing the Vinted page. If that doesn't work, ensure
            the extension is enabled in your Chrome browser's extension manager
            (you can type <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded text-sm"
              >chrome://extensions</code
            > in your address bar). If you still have trouble, please reach out to
            our support team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 text-left transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-gray-300"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">
            How do I manage my subscription or change my plan?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            You can view all our available plans on the
            <a
              href="pricing.html"
              class="font-medium underline decoration-indigo-200 hover:decoration-indigo-600 transition-colors"
              >Pricing page</a
            >. To manage an active subscription, click on the AutoLister AI
            extension icon in your browser toolbar and click Manage
            Subscription.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 text-left transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-gray-300"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">
            Is AutoLister AI officially affiliated with Vinted?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
            No, AutoLister AI is an independent, third-party tool created to
            help sellers be more successful and efficient. We are not officially
            affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Vinted in any way.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-white p-12 rounded-[20px] border border-gray-200 text-center max-w-[700px] mx-auto mt-16 shadow-sm"
      >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Still Need Help?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg mb-8 max-w-[500px] mx-auto">
          Our support team is ready to assist you. Don't hesitate to reach out
          with any questions, issues, or feedback. We'd love to hear from you!
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:support@autolister.app"
          class="inline-block bg-indigo-600 text-white px-9 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold shadow-[0_4px_15px_rgba(79,70,229,0.3)] transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-indigo-700 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_8px_25px_rgba(79,70,229,0.4)]"
        >
          Email Our Support Team
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
